<h2>The problem - you don't know how much effort it requires, and how much benefit you get</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Uncertainty</strong>: No one knows when a project finishes, and how much time you can save after the project is delivered.</li>
  <li><strong>Quantitative Analysis</strong>: There has been numerous researches and experiments for "qualitative" analysis, and a lot of best practices have been discovered.</li>
</ul>

